<subSubSection id="79DA65243625FC07C482DDE5FEAEB38E" pageId="28" pageNumber="393" type="description">
<paragraph id="317F36AF3625FC07C482DDE5FEAEB38E" blockId="28.[178,1086,218,387]" pageId="28" pageNumber="393">
Comment: The original description of 
<taxonomicName id="F6C04D2C3625FC07C6A0DDE4FCB3B2FD" authorityName="Bernhauer" authorityYear="1902" box="[656,796,218,240]" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Oxypoda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="28" pageNumber="393" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="pubescens">
<emphasis id="03B4EABD3625FC07C6A0DDE4FCB3B2FD" box="[656,796,218,240]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="393">O. pubescens</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is based on 
<specimenCount id="27C6FD263625FC07C79EDDE4FB92B2FD" box="[942,1085,218,240]" pageId="28" pageNumber="393" type="generic">one specimen</specimenCount>
collected &quot;vermuthlich aus der Umgebung von Genua&quot; deposited in the Bernhauer collection and several additional specimens &quot;von Genua&quot; deposited &quot;in der Sammlung Dodero's&quot; (
<bibRefCitation id="55514B5E3625FC07C515DC0DFE4EB345" author="BERNHAUER M" box="[293,481,306,328]" pageId="28" pageNumber="393" pagination="87 - 284" refId="ref20206" refString="BERNHAUER M. (1902): Die Staphyliniden der palaarktischen Fauna. I. Tribus: Aleocharini. (II. Theil). - Verhandlungen der Kaiserlich-Koniglichen Zoologisch-Botanischen Gesellschaft in Wien 52 (Beiheft): 87 - 284." type="journal article" year="1902">BERNHAUER 1902</bibRefCitation>
). The specimen from the Bernhauer collection, a female, is designated as the 
<typeStatus id="EE7B880D3625FC07C557DC70FE68B368" box="[359,455,335,357]" pageId="28" pageNumber="393">lectotype</typeStatus>
. It is conspecific and placed in synonymy with 
<taxonomicName id="F6C04D2C3625FC07C79CDC6FFF53B38E" authority="(HEER)" baseAuthorityName="Heer" baseAuthorityYear="1841" class="Insecta" family="Staphylinidae" genus="Oxypoda" kingdom="Animalia" order="Coleoptera" pageId="28" pageNumber="393" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="carbonaria">
<emphasis id="03B4EABD3625FC07C79CDC6FFB91B368" box="[940,1086,335,357]" italics="true" pageId="28" pageNumber="393">O. carbonaria</emphasis>
(HEER)
</taxonomicName>
.
</paragraph>
